description.en-us: Jack Hammer Debut series AcceleRacers: Metal Maniacs Produced 2005 - Present Designer Larry Wood Number G8105\n\nJack Hammer is an original design by Larry Wood that first debuted under the Metal Maniacs subset of the AcceleRacers series in 2005 . It depicts a "1950s Buick" with blown engine features, 500 HP, a stroked big block V8 to A 502ci motor with fuel-injected RAM air, four link solid rear axle, 18" front and 22" back wheels.
